 the needy provokes his Maker: but he that honors him has pity upon the poor. }{\insrsid15429465 32.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The ungodly shall be driven away in }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931 his wickedness}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
: but he who is secure in his own holiness is just. }{\insrsid15429465 33.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  There is wisdom in the good heart of a man: but in the heart of fools it }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931 is not}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 discerned. }{\insrsid15429465 34.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Righteousness exalts a nation: but sins diminish tribes. }{\insrsid15429465 35.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  An understanding servant is acceptable to a king; and by }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931 his good}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  behavior he removes disgrace. }{\insrsid15429465 1.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Anger slays even wise men; yet a submissive answer turns away wrath: but a grievous word }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931 stirs up}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  anger. }{\insrsid15429465 2.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The tongue of the wise knows what is good: but the mouth of the foolish tells out evil things. }{\insrsid15429465 3.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The eyes of the Lord behold}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 both the evil and the good in every place. }{\insrsid15429465 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
