\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 handful? Who has weighed the mourning in scales, and the forests in a balance? }{\insrsid15429465 13.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Who has known the mind of the Lord? and who has}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 been his counselor, to instruct him? }{\insrsid15429465 14.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Or with whom has he taken counsel, and he has instructed him? or who has taught him judgment,}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 or who has taught him the way of understanding ; }{\insrsid15429465 15.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  since all the nations are counted as a drop from a bucket, and as the turning of a}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 balance, [and] shall be counted as spittle? }{\insrsid15429465 16.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Libanus is not enough to burn, nor all beasts enough for a whole burnt offering; }{\insrsid15429465 17.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  and}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 all the nations are as nothing, and counted as nothing. }{\insrsid15429465 18.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 To whom have ye compared the Lord? and with what likeness have ye}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 compared him? }{\insrsid15429465 19.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 Has not the artificer made an image, or the goldsmith having melted gold, gilt it over, [and] made it a similitude? }{\insrsid15429465 20.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 For the artificer choos
es out a wood that will not rot, and will wisely inquire how he shall set up his image, and [that so] that it should not}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 be moved. }{\insrsid15429465 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 Will ye not know? will ye not hear? has it not been told you of old? Have ye not known the foundations of the earth? }{\insrsid15429465 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
[It is] he that comprehends the circle of the earth, and the inhabitants in it are as grasshoppers; he that set up the heaven as a chamber, and}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 stretched [it] out as a tent to dwell in: }{
\insrsid15429465 23.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  that appoints princes to rule as nothing, and has made the earth as nothing. }{\insrsid15429465 24.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  For they shall not}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 plant, neither shall they sow, neither shall their root be fixed in the ground: he has blown upon them, and they are withered, and a storm}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
shall carry them away like sticks. }{\insrsid15429465 25.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Now then to whom have ye compared me, that I may be exalted? saith the Holy One. }{\insrsid15429465 26.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Lift up}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 your eyes on high, and see, who has displayed all these things? [even] he that brings forth his host by number: he shall call them all by name}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 by [means of his] great glory, and by the power of his might: nothing has escaped thee. }{\insrsid15429465 27.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  For say not thou, O Jacob, and why hast thou}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 spoken, Israel, [saying], My way is hid from God, and my God has taken away [my] judgment, and has departed? }{\insrsid15429465 28.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And now, hast}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 thou not known? hast thou not heard? the eternal God, the God that formed the ends of the earth, shall not hunger, nor be weary, and}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
there is no searching of his understanding. }{\insrsid15429465 29.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  He gives strength to the hungry, and sorrow to them that are not suffering. }{\insrsid15429465 30.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  For the young}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 [men] shall hunger, and the youths shall be weary, and the choice [men] shall be powerless: but they that wait on God shall renew [their]}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 strength; they shall put forth new feathers like eagles; they shall run, and not be weary; they shall walk, and not hunger.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
