 And after these things the word of the Lord came to Abram in a vision, saying, Fear not, Abram, I shield thee, thy reward shall be very}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 great. }{\insrsid15429465 2.}{
