\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 Somoron servant shall succeed me. }{\insrsid15429465 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And immediately there was a voice of the Lord to him, saying, This shall not be thine heir but he that}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931 
 }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 shall come out of thee shall be thine heir. }{\insrsid15429465 5.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And he brought him out and said to him, Look up now to heaven, and count the stars, if thou}{
