}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 midst, and set them opposite to each other, but the birds he did not divide. }{\insrsid15429465 11.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And birds came down upon the bodies, even upon the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 divided parts of them, and Abram sat down by them. }{\insrsid15429465 12.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And about sunset a trance fell upon Abram, and lo! a great gloomy terror falls}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
