 }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 this, they shall come forth hither with much property. }{\insrsid15429465 15.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  But thou shalt depart to thy fathers in peace, nourished in a good old age.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }
