}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The sacrifices of the ungodly are an}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 abomination to the Lord; but the prayers of them that walk honestly are acceptable with him. }{\insrsid15429465 9.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The ways of an ungodly man are an}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 abomination to the Lord; but he loves those that follow after righteousness. }{\insrsid15429465 10.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The instruction of the simple is known by them that pass}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 by; but they that hate reproofs die disgracefully. }{\insrsid15429465 11.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Hell and destruction are manifest to the Lord; how shall not also be the hearts of men?}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\insrsid15429465 12.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 An uninstructed person will not love those that reprove him; neither will he associate with the wise. }{\insrsid15429465 13.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  When the heart rejoices the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
countenance is cheerful; but when it is in sorrow, the countenance is sad. }{\insrsid15429465 14.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  An upright heart seeks discretion; but the mouth of the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
uninstructed will experience evils. }{\insrsid15429465 15.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The eyes of the wicked are always looking for evil things; but the good are always quiet. }{\insrsid15429465 16.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Better}{
