n it, and gives breath to the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 people on it, and spirit to them that tread on it: }{\insrsid15429465 6.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
