\insrsid15429465 7.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  to open the eyes of the blind, to bring the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 bound and them that sit in darkness out of bonds and the prison house. }{\insrsid15429465 8.
}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  I am the Lord God: that is my name: I will not give to another,}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 nor my praises to graven images. }{\insrsid15429465 9.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 Behold, the ancient things have come to pass, and [so will] the new things which I tell you: yea, before}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 I tell [them] they are made known to you. }{\insrsid15429465 10.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Sing a new hymn to the Lord: ye his dominion, glorify his name from the end of the earth: ye}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 that go down to the sea, and sail upon
 it: the islands, and they that dwell in them. }{\insrsid15429465 11.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Rejoice, thou wilderness, and the villages thereof, the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
hamlets, and the dwellers in Kedar: the inhabitants of the rock shall rejoice, they shall shout from the top of the mountains. }{\insrsid15429465 12.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  They shall}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 give glory to God, [and] shall proclaim his praises in the islands. }{\insrsid15429465 13.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The Lord God of hosts shall go forth, and crush the war; he shall stir}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 up jealousy, and shall shout mightily against his enemies. }{\insrsid15429465 14.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  I have been silent: shall I also always be silent 
and forbear: I have endured like}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 a travailing [woman]: I will [now] amaze and wither at once. }{\insrsid15429465 15.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 I will make desolate mountains and hills, and will dry up all their grass:}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 and I will make the rivers islands, and dry up the pools. }{\insrsid15429465 16.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 And I will bring the blind by a way that they knew not, and I will cause them}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
to tread paths which they have not known: I will turn darkness into light for them, and crooked things into straight. These things will I do,}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 and will not forsake them. 
