 He who is skillful in business finds good: but he that trusts in God is most blessed. }{\insrsid15429465 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Men call the wise and}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
