}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The heart of the wise will discern the things which proceed from his own mouth; and on his lips he will wear}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 knowledge. }{\insrsid15429465 24.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Good words are honeycombs, and the sweetness thereof is a healing of the soul. }{\insrsid15429465 25.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  There are ways that seem to be right}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
