\insrsid15429465 32.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A man}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 slow to anger is better than a strong man; and he that governs his temper better than the that takes a city. }{\insrsid15429465 
