 And it came to pass after these things that God tempted Abraam, and said to him, Abraam, Abraam; and he said, Lo! I am here. }{\insrsid15429465 2.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
And he said, Take thy son, the beloved one, whom thou hast loved -- Isaac, and go into the high land, and offer him there for a whole}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
burnt offering on one of the mountains which I will tell thee of. }{\insrsid15429465 3.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam rose up in the morning and saddled his ass, and he took}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
with him two servants, and Isaac his son, and having split wood for a whole burnt offering, he arose and departed, and came to the place}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 of which God spoke to him,}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\insrsid15429465 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  on the third day; and Abraam having lifted up his eyes, saw the place afar off. }{\insrsid15429465 5.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam said to his}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 servants, Sit ye here with the ass, and I and the lad will proceed thus far, and having worshipped we will return to you. }{\insrsid15429465 6.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 took the wood of the whole burnt offering, and laid it on Isaac his son, and he took into his hands both the fire and the knife, and the two}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 went together. }{\insrsid15429465 7.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Isaac said to Abraam his father Father. And he said, What is it, son? And he said, Behold the fire and the wood,}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 where is the sheep for a whole burnt offering? }{\insrsid15429465 8.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam said, God will provide himself a sheep for a whole burnt offering, my son.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 And both having gone together, }{\insrsid15429465 9.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  came to the place which God spoke of to him and there Abraam built the altar and laid the wood on it,}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 and having bound the feet of Isaac his son together, he laid him on the altar upon the wood. }{\insrsid15429465 10.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam stretched forth his hand to}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 take the knife to slay his son. }{\insrsid15429465 11.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And an angel of the Lord called him out of heaven, and said Abraam, Abraam. And he said, Behold, I}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 am here. }{\insrsid15429465 12.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And he said, Lay not thine hand upon the child, neither do anything to him, for now I know that thou fearest God, and for my}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }
{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 sake thou}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 hast not spared thy beloved son. }{\insrsid15429465 13.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 And Abraam lifted up his eyes and beheld, and lo! a ram caught by his horns in a plant of}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 Sabec; and Abraam went and took the ram, and offered him up for a whole burnt offering i
n the place of Isaac his son. }{\insrsid15429465 14.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
called the name of that place, The Lord hath seen; that they might say to-day, In the mount the Lord was seen. }{\insrsid15429465 15.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And an angel of the}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
Lord called Abraam the second time out of heaven, saying, I have sworn by myself, says the Lord, because thou}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 hast done this thing, and}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 on my account hast not spared thy beloved son, }{\insrsid15429465 16.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  surely blessing I will bless thee, and multiplying I will multiply thy seed as the stars of}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 heaven, and as the sand which is by the shore of the sea, and thy seed shall inherit the cities of their enemies. }{\insrsid15429465 17.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 in thy seed shall all}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 the nations of the earth be blessed, because thou hast hearkened to my voice. }{\insrsid15429465 18.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  And Abraam returned to his servants, and they arose}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 and went together to the well of the oath; and Abraam dwelt at the well of the oath.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
