\par }\pard \s21\qj \li0\ri0\sl300\slmult1\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid15360938 {\insrsid15429465 17.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Have thou a friend for every time, and let brethren be useful in distress; for on this account are they born. 
}{\insrsid15429465 18.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A foolish man applauds}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 and rejoices over himself, as he also that becomes surety would make himself responsible for his own friends. 
}{\insrsid15429465 19.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A lover of sin rejoices in}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 strifes; }{\insrsid15429465 20.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 and the hard-hearted man comes not in for good. A man of a changeful tongue will fall into mischiefs; }{\insrsid15429465 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  and the heart of a fool}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
is grief to its possessor. A father rejoices not over an uninstructed son; but a wise son gladdens his mother. }{\insrsid15429465 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A glad heart promotes}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
health; but the bones of a sorrowful man dry up. }{\insrsid15429465 23.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The ways of a man who unjustly receives gifts in his bosom do not prosper; and an}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
ungodly man perverts the ways of righteousness. }{\insrsid15429465 24.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  The countenance of a wise man is sensible; but the eyes of a fool go to the ends of}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
the earth. }{\insrsid15429465 25.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A foolish son is a cause of anger to his father, and grief to her that bore him. }{\insrsid15429465 26.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  It is not right to punish a righteous man, nor}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 is it holy to plot against righteous princes. }{\insrsid15429465 27.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  He that forbears to utter a hard word is discreet, and a patient man is wise. }{
\insrsid15429465 28.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  Wisdom}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 shall be imputed to a fool who asks after wisdom: and he who holds his peace shall seem to be sensible. }{\insrsid15429465 1.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A man who wishes to separate}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 from friends seeks excuses; but at all times he will be liable to reproach. }{\insrsid15429465 2.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A senseless man feels no need of wisdom, for he is rather led}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 by folly. }{\insrsid15429465 3.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 When an ungodly man comes into a depth of evils, he despises them; but dishonor and reproach come upon him.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\insrsid15429465 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  A word in}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 the heart of a man is a deep water, and a river and fountain of life spring forth.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\insrsid15429465 5.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 
 It is not good to accept the person of the ungodly, nor is}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid16018931  }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465 it holy to pervert justice in judgment. 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid15429465 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15429465  
